**UTORG** is a fintech company holding VASP licenses and operating in 187 countries. We build digital products at the intersection of DeFi and TradFi, leveraging the world's cutting-edge technology.

Now, we are looking for a **experienced Information Security Specialist** who will strengthen our team and contribute to the success of our products and the bright future of Web3.
**What you are expected to do
**
‚óè Evaluate, implement, and manage security systems and products;
‚óè Monitor and respond to emerging security issues, threats, and trends;
‚óè Executes necessary security reconfigurations;
‚óè Integrates emerging security standards and protocols;
‚óè Develops tools to monitor and counter emerging threats;
‚óè Lead technical assessments and response during security incidents;
‚óè Communicate incident updates to management;
‚óè Design and deliver Security Awareness training to staff;
‚óè Addresses security breaches by applying fixes and security patches;
‚óè Responsible for the implementation and maintenance of PCI DSS and GDPR compliance systems.

**The Skills and Experience You Bring:
**
‚óè Availability of security certification;
‚óè Good understanding of developing and implementing system security policies based on best practices;
‚óè English proficiency of at least C1.

**Why join us?

**As a promising and ambitious team, we are flexible and open to new ideas. We are not a corporation, so everyone can influence the project. Our culture is based on empathy, innovation, and out-of-the-box thinking. We are looking for people with unique perspectives and diverse backgrounds.

**Being a part of the team means:
**
‚óè Millions of people across the world will see the results of your work;
‚óè You will engage with world-leading companies;
‚óè Budget for professional development (training programs of your choice);
‚óè Flexible working hours;
‚óè We are fully remote;
‚óè Paid vacation and sick leave;
‚óè Frequent bonuses for good performance.

You can apply for a vacancy at **https://utorg.bamboohr.com/careers/47**

